Adrienne Dore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adrienne_Dore 0 Adrienne Dore (May 23, 1910 – November 26, 1992) was an American model and beauty pageant winner. She was first runner up in the Miss America 1925 pageant, competing as Miss Los Angeles. Adrienne Dore was also an actress and went on to have modest career in motion pictures.
